### Создание заказа
POST http://localhost:5185/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userEmail": "test@example.com",
  "items": [
    {
      "id": "product-123",
      "name": "Футболка",
      "price": 5990,
      "quantity": 2,
      "images": ["https://example.com/image1.jpg"]
    }
  ]
}

### Получение заказов по email
GET http://localhost:5185/api/orders?email=test@example.com
